This project was completed as part of the Maven Analytics Power BI Desktop course, which follows a project-based learning approach. While learning Power BI concepts step by step, I worked on the AdventureWorks Cycles case study and built a business intelligence dashboard from raw data.

AdventureWorks Cycles is a fictional manufacturing company that sells cycling equipment and accessories. The main goal of this project was to transform raw business data into interactive Power BI reports for KPI tracking, regional performance comparison, product-level analysis, and customer insights.

